{"type":null,"faqId":47396,"title":"如何向主屏幕添加日历小组件？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.40347221in;}\n.s2{color:#333333;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.1930555in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span class=\"s2\">在主屏幕，长按空白区域。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span class=\"s2\">点击“窗口小工具”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span class=\"s2\">选择“日历”小工具，然后将其拖动到要添加的屏幕缩略图中。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=175849\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">主屏幕中需有足够的空间来放置窗口小工具，如果空间不足，手机将自动在屏幕面板的右侧增加一个新的主屏幕，以放置窗口小工具。手机主屏幕最多可以增加至九个。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 4  </span><span class=\"s2\">点击 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=175850\" style=\"width:0.22986111in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s2\">，返回主屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2980","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219306000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":55,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"主屏幕,添加,日历","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}